      <h2>
        Welcome to New Beginnings.
      </h2>
      <p>
        Unless you mistakenly stumbled across us by accident, it is likely to you found us because you are looking for something specific.
      </p>
      <p>
        You may be an individual looking for your next move in your current career, or perhaps a complete change of direction. You may be a business looking for a new way to attract the right people into your organisation. In either case, the decisions you are needing to make at this point in time represent a new beginning and, as our name suggests, we are here to help.
      </p>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="storyboard">
          <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-2">
              <%= image_tag("NB_stroyboard-02.jpg", class: "avatar-bordered") %>
